          "action": "Mix the mushrooms with 75ml of olive oil, 1 crushed garlic clove, 0.25 tsp of ground cinnamon, 5g of flaked sea salt, and a good grind of black pepper. Spread out on a large parchment-lined baking tray and roast for 15min, stirring halfway, until soft and starting to brown.",
